X_test : X Test dataset
X_train: X Train dataset
Y_train: Y train dataset
Y_test: Y Test dataset
subject_test: Subject test dataset
subject_train: Subject train dataset
features: features dataset
X: Appended X train and test dataset
Y: Appended Y train and test dataset
subject: Appended Y train and test dataset
data - merge of all the features, activity and subject
data_mean : Extract only mean columns
data_std: Extract std columns
Activity: Data with activity info
Subject: Data with subject info
data_mean_std: Dataset with mean, standard deviation, activity names and subject columns
tidy_data: Final tidy dataset with mean for all the columns at Acitivy name and subject level
